{
  "stem": "21626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he was thrown into a hostel like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And his name was Joe, Joe [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Placek. ?] And he was-- he was a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he turned up at Auntie's store one night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was unshaven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He was dirty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He was hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he was a bit drunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I was so shocked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But these people, you see-- they thought they were doing him a favor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They gave him-- they treated him like one of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And Auntie was horrified to see him in that state.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So of course, she fed him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Then she took all his clothes off of him, and put an old track suit of mine on him, and told me to take him to the communal baths while she washed all her floors.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And she said, you can stay the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he stayed the night and remained with us for a whole month.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I never heard from him since.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I never heard of him till many years later, when I learned that he made his way to Moravia with another man-- well, another boy from our school.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Again, another orphan who came Slovakia, actually-- and there they were taught to fly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There was some-- and I think it was-- it was a Jewish-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But there was some commission there sent from Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But any way, they were taught to fly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they came-- then they went to Israel on one of the ships and fought in the Israeli war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they more or less founded the Israeli Air Force, and trained the pilots, and became incredible, incredible names in Israel Air Force.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
